{"tid":1727180,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[集思廣益] 和理非式開花有冇得諗？","createTime":"2019-11-16T10:55:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-16T12:23:14.000Z","uid":56693,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"2ed9bcbb76d66c4a84d317a8f958d8e57bdac899","tid":1727180,"uid":56693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T10:55:56.000Z","msg":"過去一個禮拜前線手足好辛苦成功幫我地罷左工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n作為和理非除左幫手塞鐵 同 和你lunch之外其實係咪可以做多啲？<br />\n之前政府咁急各區大規模咁清就知佢地有幾驚連儂牆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n除左會將資訊更流傳到比藍絲/淺黃/唔識上網嘅公公婆婆知之外 亦可以時刻提住健忘嘅香港人 我地已經犧牲太多 係無路可退<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 宜家我地有好多有利嘅材料喺手 包括出老解 popo射tg企圖慢性毒死香港人等等 唔可以白白浪費<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />順便建立返我地嘅正面形象 鞏固民心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n幾丁友貼文宣又會擔心安全問題 不如試下各區和理非搵個時間一齊聚集 和理非式開花喺自己區重建連儂牆？咁大家往後都可以組隊恆常化咁更新<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n不過擔心黑警趕盡殺絕 最後變各區和你送頭行動<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但係我覺得文宣一定繼續要做落去同前線行動配合先得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申：蠢  只係想幫多啲手 唔啱屌細力啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"a017169c0d0d4343bb70399a076137c1b6e54473","tid":1727180,"uid":761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T10:57:19.000Z","msg":"推手"},{"pid":"2dd7e66f29b59210c45739173e46c2d184f95cfb","tid":1727180,"uid":56693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T10:58:45.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"8bdd875e1a68daa326969b2e8a2f7c11a99c6787","tid":1727180,"uid":56693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T10:58:56.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"f9fdd4c6607ae5bb60b913254fcd7101ffc05a78","tid":1727180,"uid":56693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"scor