w.pori.hk%2F&d=VpJPAaQEVg4A3L06AjdBQAZxBlA1GgcQN30t83kccHY%3D&h=b91f91fa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.pori.hk/</a><br />\n<br />\n(對唔住，咁危難時刻下我知而家仲叫大家課金可能好反感，但我相信兄弟爬山，各有各做，行得通就全力去做<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)"},{"pid":"701df546d8f85e1a9099ef45c1f2bb6a1ab1f399","tid":1727180,"uid":259329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T11:10:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4465defcee80f5b7e7a38060b1b2c44607eb9d71","tid":1727180,"uid":30251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T11:13:13.000Z","msg":"文宣文宣"},{"pid":"e5ff056f35053d1d2e18cdd4b18915f08faa112b","tid":1727180,"uid":56693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T11:15:21.000Z","msg":"港豬：老解真係做實事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01894542be7c3d2026f21b8590acab73c1218be9","tid":1727180,"uid":56693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T11:31:52.000Z","msg":"淺黃：點解要罷工？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a1286d3016db1467120452be7d1a2e01fc58eab","tid":1727180,"uid":189404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T12:03:13.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"132d3fd0f5c7ffdba863c0af00e19d6441cdcb71","tid":1727180,"uid":12773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T12:04:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fee4534015aab007cfa7fedc4fceb3baff060d02","tid":1727180,"uid":71197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T12:06:44.000Z","msg":"Tui"}]}